{"GYL55LzMnmd":{"id":"GYL55LzMnmd","type":"work","title":"金鎞秘論","authors":[{"name":"谿流寓李藥師","role":"撰","dynasty":"梁"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《金鎞秘論》•十二卷","author_info":"舊本題梁谿流寓李藥師撰","summary":"舊本題梁谿流寓李藥師撰。不知何許人。自序稱唐李靖以三等法教士，故亦以三等法治病。藥師之稱，適符靖字，殆亦寓名歟？其書分十二門，皆論醫目之法，故曰《金鎞》，蓋取佛書金鎞刮眼之義也。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12}},"GYL55LwSW4P":{"id":"GYL55LwSW4P","type":"work","title":"簡明醫彀","authors":[{"name":"孫志宏","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《簡明醫彀》•八卷","author_info":"明孫志宏撰","summary":"明孫志宏撰。志宏字台石，杭州人。是書卷首冠要言一十六則，議論亦平正。其餘案門列方，淺顯易解，然未能盡醫道之變化也。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":8},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/簡明醫彀","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=851115","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4023741","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-keben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02055065","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刻本","version":"v4","total_page":915,"paragraph_count":7340,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL55LtUXVh":{"id":"GYL55LtUXVh","type":"work","title":"針灸節要","authors":[{"name":"高武","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《針灸節要》•三卷","author_info":"明高武撰","summary":"明高武撰。是書以《難經》、《素問》為主。《難經》首取行針補瀉，次取井榮俞經合，次及經脈。《素問》首九針，次補瀉，次諸法，次病刺，次經脈空穴。俱顛倒後先，於經文多割裂。","edition":"兩淮鹽政采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":3},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=200601","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-kanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA06096","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本(序刊)","version":"v12","total_page":630,"paragraph_count":735,"has_translation":true,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"sh